00:16:02,538 --> 00:16:06,937
Well, don't you want to know how to solve the cipher?

277
00:16:06,938 --> 00:16:09,337
No, that can wait.

278
00:16:09,338 --> 00:16:13,237
Since that cipher was made by Mr. Kusukawa, the gambling man,

279
00:16:13,238 --> 00:16:17,738
