298
00:17:16,038 --> 00:17:18,437
The red dots of dice are bigger and striking,

299
00:17:18,438 --> 00:17:21,137
now you can read the seven numbers.

300
00:17:21,138 --> 00:17:25,437
The number comes up to 3156204.

301
00:17:25,438 --> 00:17:30,938
So, it's 3156204.

302
00:17:31,838 --> 00:17:34,137
Probably, the cipher was made into squares

303
00:17:34,138 --> 00:17:36,337
with the center to be nine

304
00:17:36,338 --> 00:17:40,337
because of the image of dice and dots on them.

305
00:17:40,338 --> 00:17:42,538
Look! It's opened.

306
00:17:44,038 --> 00:17:47,238
So, this is it. The tape you wanted to get.

